{"tid":1815643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先上左小巴","createTime":"2020-01-07T16:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T16:08:20.000Z","uid":74688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cf68f1d61ba8c88c852d152ecd99ca9d2b4b196c","tid":1815643,"uid":74688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:06:55.000Z","msg":"頭先上小巴，一上去門口對住個位坐左兩個麻甩佬。<br />\n其中一個話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:阿X去左邊<br />\n另一個好認真咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:去左搵彩虹掛<br />\n我以為佢講笑，心諗男人老狗搵乜鬼彩虹。<br />\n另一個人居然又好認真咁問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:附近有彩虹架咩<br />\n另一個又認真答返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:隔離街好似有彩虹<br />\n我就喺度諗，彩虹會唔會係d咩江湖術語,或者架步之類<br />\n然後突然間有第三個男人上車，之前個兩個麻甩佬問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:無彩虹咩<br />\n上車個人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:無呀，去左黃大仙先<br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612c69a52a916c9d4e723b95228a0e17d4d6bd1c","tid":1815643,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:08:20.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆"}]}